{"tid":1610410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實今日香港已經變咗大陸","createTime":"2019-10-01T17:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T09:03:40.000Z","uid":199237,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5ef44f2ea9465c18c5830cb55850a3b6c868025d","tid":1610410,"uid":199237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:23:29.000Z","msg":"大陸十一成個北京全面封鎖<br />\n唔比任何人出街<br />\n唔比任何人買賣利器<br />\n<br />\n今日香港<br />\n唔比你出黎訴求<br />\n你出黎就搜你身 搵到任何野都可以屈你入罪<br />\n<br />\n就好似中共告你煽動顛覆國家政權咁莫須有<br />\n<br />\n根本今日就代表咗中共正式損害<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港自治</span>"},{"pid":"2e60f4e853b937e351f314e750d99854b4357c0b","tid":1610410,"uid":199237,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"推 幫中五學生祈禱"},{"pid":"4aec380fba2c564576ebe23fce68687ae89f17ed","tid":1610410,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:23:50.000Z","msg":"請全民無&middot;限&middot;期罷工罷課，救自己、救義士！迫政府讓步！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"623400496fdd54dd7a450d98759c1b9734c1e674","tid":1610410,"uid":199237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:24:01.000Z","msg":"仲要為十一而開實彈"},{"pid":"5361ca6d2a3cff0b681746d0f75f465d6dd81e3f","tid":1610410,"uid":199237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:24:21.000Z","msg":"咁咪代表中共破壞香港自治"},{"pid":"208e98e71f1c5c6dc190f07176efbd89d8f3b315","tid":1610410,"uid":199237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:25:26.000Z","msg":"幫手推plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/